The incident happened on Thursday afternoon near the Fulton County Courthouse in downtown Atlanta .
Police were investigating a call about a stolen car when they saw Alexia Christian, 25, sitting in the back of a cop car in a parking deck .
At one point she fired at the officers, and they returned fire, critically wounding her .
She was taken to Grady Memorial Hospital but died from her injuries .
Eyewitnesses said she had been handcuffed and must have somehow got one hand free to fire a gun while in the patrol car .